NeighborhoodHideSeek.ABOUT_BLURB = [[Neighborhood Hide & Seek is to help you run a game of hide and seek with a group of friends in your neighborhood. The party/raid leader keeps the game running and moves through the phases. When a game session starts, the leader chooses whether rounds draw from the current neighborhood list, their saved house list, or the group’s members (visit each plot from Housing). In each round a house, game mode, and seeker(s) are picked. As a group decide if the group is hiding inside or outside of the house.]]
